onductors. Recent advancements in colloidal chemistry indicate that these\nmaterials can be synthesized from semiconductor nanocrystals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Feb 2015 13:18:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Feb 2015 09:15:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-19"}
