 from the nova ejecta. We have\nalso estimated the range for the ejecta mass in V2468 Cyg to be 3 x 10^{-6} -\n10^{-5} Msun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Feb 2015 15:13:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
